6.11	Twistin'_the_Night_Away	Twistin' the Night Away	"Twistin' the Night Away" is a song written and recorded by Sam Cooke. It was released as a single in 1962 and became very popular, charting in the top ten of both the Billboard Hot 100 (#9) and Billboard's R&amp;B chart (#1),. "Twistin' the Night Away" was successful overseas as well, peaking at #6 on the UK Singles Chart.	
